    {
      "id": "9317171f-3b80-48f8-9b9b-b1524ac4b7c8",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "ITS predict likely student answers and provide individualized feedback but, most Knowledge Tracing tasks focus on getting question right or wrong and do not focus explicitly on knowledge states of the learner.",
